name: Smolest Natural Glitch
description: This smol animated GIF is based on video footage of mine. The recording shows the surface of the seawater of my island. The crystal clear waters allow also the light to penetrate the surface and reach down to the bottom of the sea. Light and water in a dance of distortion of bottoms image, creating shapes and cirles, magnifiying image and light. Created with Premiere and Photoshop edititng. George Angelis 2021
